import React from 'react'
import classes from './WeightForm.module.css'

function WeightForm() {
    return(
        <form className = {classes.form}>
            <label for="date-of-tracking"  className = {classes.date}>Date of Tracking the Weight:</label>
            <input type= "date" id="dot" name="dot"/>
            <label for="weight" className = {classes.weight}>Weight (in Kilos)</label>
            <input type= "number" min= "0" step= "0.01" />
            <button className = {classes.submit}>Add Data</button>
        </form>
    )
}

export default WeightForm
